## ğŸ’¡ How It Works
1ï¸âƒ£ **Convert Image to Grayscale** (removes colors)  
2ï¸âƒ£ **Invert Colors** (to create a negative effect)  
3ï¸âƒ£ **Apply Gaussian Blur** (to create smooth shading)  
4ï¸âƒ£ **Blend with Original Image** (to generate pencil effect)  

